name: Darkside of John
description:
As their ship settled in orbit of the 4th moon, Lucy was relieved, 'Tz-Crash-1331' was still flowing, not in her body but in her soul.John was watching the glowing colors that were  remnants of the planet destroyed by the first ones, it was a beautiful yet melancholic sight. John always had a dark side,he had already lost his faith in humanity ,in the past,and his faith in Gods. He used to believe the 'they' would save the planet,but then he lost all his faith in them when he saw what they did. The strange history of this planet was the cause of his troubled mind.

“What do you think ?” asked Lucy.

“I don’t know…  their history is complicated.”

“So there are 4 planets that were destroyed by the ‘first’ people?”

“Yep,” said John as he looked at Lucy.

“I know the history of your planet,so I don’t understand,” said Lucy.

“We destroyed the ‘first’ planet.Then,2 of our race came here and destroyed the second planet,then 3 people came here and destroyed the third planet. First people came here to look after us,but they left a bunch of different creatures here to live on the 5th planet,but then one of them was nasty..."

Lucy asked Daedalus to take some snapshots from her visual cortex, she had never seen John like this before | @atimtay | linktr.ee/atimtakus
